data.description: Great opportunity for an owner occupied or sole investment property with gorgeous panoramic views of the Helderbergs. This ranch style duplex sits on a sprawling 5 acres. Owner has updated kitchen, bathrooms, doors, moldings, 1000 sq ft wrap around deck, and all new floors in the last few years. Each unit has 2 BR, 1 Bath, spacious kitchen, dining area, spacious LR, full basements, wrap around deck, laundry/mudrooms, tons of closet space & separate utilities. Roof is 10 years young. There are two 1000 gallon concrete septic tanks (one for each unit.) Unit 2 tenant is long term and brings guaranteed income upon closing! Never missed a payment! Solar panels are owned not leased and offer HUGE savings!! This property is truly one of a kind! Excellent Condition
